  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228900/extras/8ffd542ba5da825b9ef0a8600f0391bb.avif?t=1748805944\" width=536 height=72 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228900/extras/3dd366af0f3f3a4fa0dda33cd09f0fa7.poster.avif?t=1748805944\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228900/extras/3dd366af0f3f3a4fa0dda33cd09f0fa7.webm?t=1748805944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228900/extras/3dd366af0f3f3a4fa0dda33cd09f0fa7.mp4?t=1748805944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Fight your way through the hordes of evil baddies that block your path as you forge a hero's path to defeat evil!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228900/extras/808e03370bb0cd01081360fd5d69e2f4.avif?t=1748805944\" width=536 height=72 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228900/extras/bb6e78ebffd1d3219c0ce9f7940219ff.poster.avif?t=1748805944\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228900/extras/bb6e78ebffd1d3219c0ce9f7940219ff.webm?t=1748805944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228900/extras/bb6e78ebffd1d3219c0ce9f7940219ff.mp4?t=1748805944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Face off against monstrous bosses that want nothing more than to eat you for lunch. Prepare to face varied, stompy, and quite grumpy agents of the great evil who will stop at nothing to keep you from your hero's path.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228900/extras/13046b0f4444d58dca055aedd7669aab.avif?t=1748805944\" width=536 height=72 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228900/extras/78601bd39e3d1fa99c161248aa09323c.poster.avif?t=1748805944\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228900/extras/78601bd39e3d1fa99c161248aa09323c.webm?t=1748805944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2228900/extras/78601bd39e3d1fa99c161248aa09323c.mp4?t=1748805944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><br>*Tight Character Controls<br>*Multiple Biomes to Explore<br>*Varied baddies to battle<br>*Large and angry bosses to crush<br>*Survive the hordes in special modes and levels<br>*Attempted humor and dad jokes<br>*Possibly hidden pastries<br><br>- Steam capsule artwork by AnxietyComics!",
